lyrics:
[Verse]
Tzuf, a kid so friendly and funny
But he longed to join The Polak Gang, oh so hungry
They were a group of students, smart and elite
But Tzuf's problem was he didn't meet the feat

[Chorus]
Oh, Tzuf felt the sting, oh, it cut him deep
Rejected by the Gang, he couldn't sleep
But he's got a spirit that simply won't break
Tzuf will find his place, his dreams he'll make
